    <h2 class="reveal" style="font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: clamp(28px,6vw,44px); letter-spacing: -1px; margin-bottom: 8px;">Simple. Fast.<br>Built for Nairobi.</h2>
